install blog "MAY 2013" WordPress Codex "Function Reference"
============================================================

NAME
----

install blog - Install an empty blog.

SYNOPSIS
--------

Install an empty blog.

Creates the new blog tables and options. If calling this function
directly, be sure to use switch\_to\_blog() first, so that \$wpdb points
to the new blog.

USAGE
-----

` <?php install_blog( $blog_id, $blog_title ); ?> `

PARAMETERS
----------

 `$blog_id` 
:   ([*int*](/How_to_Pass_Tag_Parameters#Int "How to Pass Tag Parameters"))
    (*required*) The value returned by insert\_blog().
    Default: *None*

 `$blog_title` 
:   ([*string*](/How_to_Pass_Tag_Parameters#String "How to Pass Tag Parameters"))
    (*optional*) The title of the new site.
    Default: empty string

CHANGE LOG
----------

Since: [MU](/Version_MU "Version MU")

SOURCE FILE
-----------

`install_blog()` is located in `wp-includes/ms-functions.php`

